race.comment: DEEP EMOTION (7) comes here deep into the campaign with the right figures to take this out from the inside draw. Shuffled back from the sticky draw and failed to run the 1600m out with a plodding  ninth at Kembla Grange. Gets map favours from the inside gate and can return to form with Latham retaining the ride. NAGADEC (9) another who jumped in trip with a disappointing sixth over 1600m at the Sapphire Coast at latest. Winning rider goes back aboard and has excellent credentials over this trip. BELLARATA (10) progressive mare who was an impressive maiden winner at start three  over 1400m at this track. Has scope for improvement and can get across from the wide draw. Sure to be thereabouts. DEEPWATER ARTIST (5) bounced off the good first-up second with a dominant on-pace victory over 1400m at the Sapphire Coast in C1 grade. Has further upside and represents good each way value.
